{"tid":2246093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒真係話嚟就嚟","createTime":"2020-10-16T18:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:02:44.000Z","uid":312893,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f81524600de130445522f45e458728d62ac58ef9","tid":2246093,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"本身keep住全日都幾好心情<br />\n一到夜晚夜深人靜 瞓唔著嘅時候啲負面情緒就出哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係聽歌會聽到個人好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同個best friend冷戰咗幾個月<br />\n呢排又聽到之前曖昧過嘅對象嘅消息 <br />\n無再聯絡好耐 但唔知點解耐唔耐都有啲掛住佢<br />\n好想知佢哋過成點<br />\n但又放唔低面子道歉先<br />\n又怕突然搵人會好odd好唐突<br />\n<br />\n我以為將注意力放喺另一班人身上就會忘記佢哋<br />\n但原來靜落嚟嘅時候<br />\n都會記返起以前同佢哋一齊相處嘅回憶<br />\n然後後悔之前無好好珍惜同維繫感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想同身邊嘅朋友傾呢啲事<br />\n唔想煩到佢哋 又驚影響埋佢哋心情<br />\n<br />\n同埋我本身就唔想同太多人交心<br />\n因為我覺得每個人都會離開我<br />\n到最後都會只係得我一個人<br />\n<br />\n可能係我個人太差<br />\n可能我根本唔配有人陪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d63053382f0ee43b1d906bead73537b120bd78","tid":2246093,"uid":177723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"樓主巴定絲"},{"pid":"f14a5c5102b30e48f01a98b6553821e3dbcce00e","tid":2246093,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"雖然夜晚好啱用黎叫春, 但你都係訓喇既然情緒咁down"},{"pid":"9fe8e77696b6d12f9000e2c48245e327e4dc6fb1","tid":2246093,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"89d63053382f0ee43b1d906bead73537b120bd78","tid":2246093,"uid":177723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"樓主巴定絲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"絲<br />\n有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c0d